{"tid":1335942,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港大太古橋大字遭淋紅油","createTime":"2019-07-20T17:19:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-20T17:19:13.000Z","uid":1108,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"76cd2537b8addf5cc24544df35b68563ee80e878","tid":1335942,"uid":1108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T17:19:13.000Z","msg":"香港大學學生刊物《學苑》報導，於晚上十二時十分左右， 有太古堂宿生發現太古橋上「冷血屠城 烈士英魂不朽 誓殲豺狼 民主星火不滅」廿字被人淋上紅油蓄意破壞。就現場所見，廿字中僅有「星火不滅」四字未被淋上紅油。<br />\n<br />\n讀者提供圖片<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C8d7vfr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC8d7vfr.jpg&h=2542ca44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kdv51m6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fkdv51m6.jpg&h=a3e4a691&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好似個幾個字真係有人流過血咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好似去左現場<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}